- I see

311
00:34:48,119 --> 00:34:50,087
"Sir, we have a problem"

312
00:34:50,455 --> 00:34:55,688
The exams start tomorrow
and Nirjara is very upset

313
00:34:56,527 --> 00:34:58,688
