314
00:34:58,930 --> 00:35:02,832
"No, actually...
- She has lost her admission card"

315
00:35:03,101 --> 00:35:06,628
I had kept it in my book.
It has gone missing

316
00:35:06,971 --> 00:35:10,168
So?
- A notice on the college board says...

317
00:35:10,508 --> 00:35:13,033
they won't allow us to appear
for the exams without the card

318
00:35:20,318 --> 00:35:22,752
You have come to me
with such a small problem?

319
00:35:23,187 --> 00:35:26,156
